data.description: This absolutely stunning two story in Blaine is a must see. The moment you walk in you’ll be blown away by the light filled living spaces, open floor plan, and impressive design elements. The main floor features a fabulous fireplace, gorgeous hardwood floors, and a modern gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs you’ll find the highly sought after 4 bedrooms, with large primary bed and bath. The lower level features a recreation room and it’s a walk out! Looking for a more places to entertain? Check out the outdoor living spaces, with a breath taking deck and patio space with pond view! Don’t miss out on this impressive move in ready home!
